Context:
The WAVE Dental Clinic is accepting registrations for dental services. New patients need to register for an appointment online, by email, or phone. COVID-19 regulations and requirements can be found on the website. Students from various dental programs (Dental Health, Dental Hygiene, Dental Assisting, Denturism, and Restorative Dental Hygiene) provide dental services at the clinic for low costs. The clinic does not offer emergency dental treatment, and services are only available during the school year, except for suspensions due to school closures or statuary holidays.
